      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. a \"trusted friend\" is probably the one who shared the screenshots in the first place. and a counselor? i feel like everyone is just watching me fail. it feels like the whole world is just one big room where everyone is laughing at me. there's no \"way forward\" when everything you do just makes it worse. it's just a constant cycle of being humiliated. i'm just so tired of existing like this.",
